Front-end
=========

1. setup proxy for debug
2. review service organization per REST resource: token, user, team, match, bet...
3. implement components in this order:
	- signin (Token, Profile)
	- menu
	- bets (Bet)
	- matches (Match)
	- time (Time)
	
Back-end
========

1. Adapt deps to include postgres
2. Setup postgres configuration
3. Install docker and docker-compose
4. Check back-end on postgres docker image

System
======

1. Prepare docker images for back-end and front-end (nginx)
2. Setup docker-compose to launch all images at once

